      <category><![CDATA[market update]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/?p=7899</guid>
      <description>Busted. The August bottom has been convincingly broken.  It did it on almost 90% down volume.  This will either continue to spiral down or set up a tradeable swing. The bottom may be as close as 1077.30.  Time will tell. &amp;#8230; &lt;a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/tonights-market-update/tonights-market-update-monday-3rd/"&gt;Continue reading &lt;span class="meta-nav"&gt;&amp;#8594;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/range-traders/Range_Traders-Tonights_Market_Update__Monday_3rd.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Busted.</p>
<p>The August bottom has been convincingly broken.  It did it on almost 90% down volume.  This will either continue to spiral down or set up a tradeable swing.</p>
<p>The bottom may be as close as 1077.30.  Time will tell.</p>
<p><span id="more-7899"></span>The best strategy has been to short when price crossed the 20d MA and short again every time it approached it from the underside.</p>
<h1><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/SP-3rd.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-7900" title="S&amp;P 3rd" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/SP-3rd-300x243.png" alt="" width="300" height="243" /></a>Tonight&#8217;s market conundrum is finding the bottom to the latest swing.</h1>
<p>Futures are mildly positive at 8:45 PST.  It&#8217;s a long time until the trading day begins in New York.  I&#8217;ll be watching and hoping to have a clearer sense of direction tomorrow night.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
]]></content:encoded>
