    <item>
      <title>Tonight’s Market Update — Thursday 22nd</title>
      <link>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/tonights-market-update/tonights-market-update-thursday-22nd/</link>
      <comments>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/tonights-market-update/tonights-market-update-thursday-22nd/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Sep 2011 03:12:56 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Range Trader</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Tonight's Market Update]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/?p=7851</guid>
      <description>It appears that the e wave is complete.  The prior low and the low before that were decidedly broken.  It&amp;#8217;s a bit early to tell, but the market may be embarking on a 5th wave. down. The market gapped lower &amp;#8230; &lt;a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/tonights-market-update/tonights-market-update-thursday-22nd/"&gt;Continue reading &lt;span class="meta-nav"&gt;&amp;#8594;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/range-traders/Range_Traders-Tonights_Market_Update__Thursday_22nd.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>It appears that the e wave is complete.  The prior low and the low before that were decidedly broken.  It&#8217;s a bit early to tell, but the market may be embarking on a 5th wave. down.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/SP-22nd.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-7852" title="S&amp;P 22nd" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/SP-22nd-300x273.png" alt="Tonight's Market" width="300" height="273" /></a><span id="more-7851"></span>The market gapped lower at today&#8217;s open and continued lower for most of the day.  For the near-future higher prices are in the rear view mirror.</p>
<p>I&#8217;m expecting a bump higher over the next day, several days, who knows.  These are the targets I&#8217;m watching for a retracement.  Aggressive traders may want to consider shorting the DIA, QQQQ, or SPY near these levels:  DJ-30  10,918ish, NASDAQ Composite 2493ish, and the S&amp;P near 1147.</p>
<p>** I hope to have the blog repaired and back to full speed in the next week or 10 days.  Fighting this hack has been a nightmare as I&#8217;ve had to field several IT calls on a daily basis.</p>
<p>I&#8217;m told this unfortunate occurence is one of the ugly sides of a high-ranking blog that posts cutting-edge content and spot on market analysis &#8212; everybody wants a piece of it in some form or another.  Nevertheless, the new endeavor will be hardened with the latest security features.</p>
<p>I look forward to restoring my trading life and the members&#8217; portion of the blog very soon.  As mentioned in an earlier post, each member that was current with their subscription when the site went down will have their membership extended for an additional month.</p>
<p>Thanks for your patience and well wishes!</p>
<p>Karen</p>
]]></content:encoded>
