      <title>Tonight’s Market Update — Wednesday 21st</title>
      <link>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/tonights-market-update/tonights-market-update-wednesday-21st/</link>
      <comments>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/tonights-market-update/tonights-market-update-wednesday-21st/#comments</comments>
