      <dc:creator>Range Trader</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Tonight's Market Update]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/?p=118</guid>
      <description>A close look at the market&amp;#8217;s internal structure reveals some strange sights.  Why are the momentum stocks blazing while financials, coals, oil stocks, and copper all sit dead in the water?  One of two things will happen &amp;#8211;  the slow &amp;#8230; &lt;a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/tonights-market-update/tonights-market-update-wednesday-21st/"&gt;Continue reading &lt;span class="meta-nav"&gt;&amp;#8594;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/range-traders/Range_Traders-Tonights_Market_Update__Wednesday_21st.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>A close look at the market&#8217;s internal structure reveals some strange sights.  Why are the momentum stocks blazing while financials, coals, oil stocks, and copper all sit dead in the water?  One of two things will happen &#8211;  the slow pokes start to level off and make gains or the go go momo stocks will start to wane.</p>
<p><span id="more-118"></span>I&#8217;ve removed the labeling from the S&amp;P to concentrate more on support and resistance levels.  The top blue line is the first area of support at 1155.  If that level falls the second level to watch is the 1125 area.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/SP-21st1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-120" title="S&amp;P 21st" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/SP-21st1-300x275.png" alt="" width="300" height="275" /></a></p>
<p>I can&#8217;t remember a time when Dr. Copper was considered an inverse indicator.  Today, it made another new low.  This is<em> not</em> bullish.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Copper21st.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-121" title="Copper21st" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Copper21st-300x274.png" alt="Range Traders" width="300" height="274" /></a></p>
<p>This market is a persistent worry between rally and death spirals.  Right now, cash is king.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
