      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The Market Timer is now positive.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Market-Timer-Th.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-93" title="Market Timer Th" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Market-Timer-Th-300x216.png" alt="Range Trading" width="300" height="216" /></a></p>
<p><span id="more-92"></span>Here is where I&#8217;d be watching for the first area of resistance &#8212; the big yellow arrow on this hourly chart.  It&#8217;s about 22 S&amp;P points higher.  Price will likely challenge that area and head for the Range Lines just overhead.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/SP-Th.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-94" title="S&amp;P Th" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/SP-Th-300x217.png" alt="Range Trader" width="300" height="217" /></a>I don&#8217;t like to trade corrective waves like the current one.  My hunch is the next wave will be down and that will be the one I&#8217;ll ride.</p>
<p>I&#8217;m forming a watch list and will post it so you can see what I&#8217;m following.</p>
<p>Stay patient!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
]]></content:encoded>
