      <description>It was a give-back day and it had some volume behind it.  Unfortunately, it was in the wrong direction &amp;#8212; down instead of up. The NASDAQ tagged the top Range resistance (pink) line and retreated on the biggest volume in &amp;#8230; &lt;a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/tonights-market-update/tonights-market-update/"&gt;Continue reading &lt;span class="meta-nav"&gt;&amp;#8594;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/range-traders/Range_Traders-Tonights_Market_Update.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>It was a give-back day and it had some volume behind it.  Unfortunately, it was in the wrong direction &#8212; down instead of up.</p>
<p>The NASDAQ tagged the top Range resistance (pink) line and retreated on the biggest volume in the last six sessions.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/NAZ1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-45" title="NAZ" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/NAZ1-300x269.png" alt="Range Trading" width="300" height="269" /></a>Neither the DJ-30 or the S&amp;P made much of a move.</p>
<p>Watch for a challenge to recent highs.  That will determine if the top is in on this brief swing higher or if there is more left to the upside</p>
