      <dc:creator>Range Trader</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/?p=7</guid>
      <description>Today, the S&amp;#38;P tagged the 1143 level and started to climb.  At the end of the day it was near the top of its range. I&amp;#8217;m sorry to say that there&amp;#8217;s little reason to be hopeful about the health of &amp;#8230; &lt;a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/uncategorized/range-trading-zones-for-wednesday/"&gt;Continue reading &lt;span class="meta-nav"&gt;&amp;#8594;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/range-traders/Range_Traders-Range_Trading_Zones_For_Wednesday.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Today, the S&amp;P tagged the 1143 level and started to climb.  At the end of the day it was near the top of its range.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/SP.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-22" title="S&amp;P" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/SP-300x258.png" alt="Range Trading Zones" width="300" height="258" /></a>I&#8217;m sorry to say that there&#8217;s little reason to be hopeful about the health of this market.  Too many political, economic, and fiscal worries not just in the USA, but worldwide.</p>
<p><span id="more-7"></span>These are the best and worst case Range Trading Zones for the three major averages:</p>
<h1>The S&amp;P</h1>
<p>A gap higher in the morning may signal a bit of strength.  The best upside case may be the 1196 level.</p>
<p>The worst case scenario happens if price breaks below the 1143.  The next Range Support zone would be 1088 on the downside.</p>
<h1>NASDAQ</h1>
<p>Best case sees price move to 2537.  That would also fill an island left during the swift decline.</p>
<p>On the downside, watch 2302.</p>
<h1>DJ-30</h1>
<p>Possible upside target 11424.</p>
<p>Downside target is 10488</p>
<p>The futures will give a hint about the opening.  Tonight they are green.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
