      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="round and round and round...." href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/45409431@N00/4130535600/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2723/4130535600_4e7ec48e6d_m.jpg" border="0" alt="round and round and round...." /></a><br />
