      <title>Not Just Bumps In The Road, But Potholes</title>
      <link>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/uncategorized/bumps-road-potholes/</link>
      <comments>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/uncategorized/bumps-road-potholes/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Jul 2011 03:58:03 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Range Trader</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Trading The Stock Market]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/?p=7407</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[photo credit: Katie Tegtmeyer I believe in trading the tape, not the news.  These days the two are tightly intertwined. Unless you like to scalp intraday I&#8217;d stand aside.  This is a market that is full of potholes. Pothole #1 &#8230; <a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/uncategorized/bumps-road-potholes/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Rough Road" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/44538772@N00/3742343779/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2656/3742343779_628074ccec_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Rough Road" /></a><br />
<small><a title="Attribution License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="Katie Tegtmeyer" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/44538772@N00/3742343779/" target="_blank">Katie Tegtmeyer</a></small></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">I believe in trading the tape, not the news.  These days the two are tightly intertwined.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Unless you like to scalp intraday I&#8217;d stand aside.  This is a market that is full of potholes.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Pothole #1 &#8212; the DJ-30 not only closes at the bottom of the daily range, but outside of the lower fork&#8217;s rail, too.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-7408" href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/current-market-news/bumps-road-potholes/attachment/dj-12/"><img class="size-medium wp-image-7408 aligncenter" title="DJ-30" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/dj-300x178.png" alt="" width="300" height="178" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Pothole #2 &#8212; The RUT has performed the same price action and closed way beyond the lower fork&#8217;s rail.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-7409" href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/current-market-news/bumps-road-potholes/attachment/rut-30/"><img class="size-medium wp-image-7409 aligncenter" title="RUT" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/rut-300x174.png" alt="" width="300" height="174" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">The U.S. dollar can&#8217;t make much headway in this environment.  It is still closing below the long-term trend line.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-7412" href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/current-market-news/bumps-road-potholes/attachment/dollar-39/"><img class="size-medium wp-image-7412" title="Dollar" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/dollar-300x175.png" alt="" width="300" height="175" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Members got a nice chunk &#8216;o change for the bank account, today.  HLX was our winner for the day popping 15% for a healthy gain as it tapped the first profit target.  Congrats to all who had a piece of HLX!</p>
<p>No new trades for me.   The ones I have are on a short leash!</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span id="more-7407"></span>The bears could have knocked this market down hard, but so far haven&#8217;t been able to do it.  The bulls are not making a very valiant effort to fight for their turf, but they are holding their ground in the face of constant, negative headlines.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Hold tight, honor stops, and this too shall pass.  Congrats to all fellow traders that had the HLX trade!</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://tinyurl.com/4d3tfoc">Trade Sheet</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
