      <link>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/charts-data-analysis/charts-data-analysis-week-july-25th/</link>
      <comments>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/charts-data-analysis/charts-data-analysis-week-july-25th/#comments</comments>
