      <description><![CDATA[Today&#8217;s market action was indecisive.  A strong start and a weak close are not the makings of a robust move, yet. Price bounced off the 50d MA and that was good to see.  There is still some big players with &#8230; <a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/trading-the-market/hold-line/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Today&#8217;s market action was indecisive.  A strong start and a weak close are not the makings of a robust move, yet.</p>
<p>Price bounced off the 50d MA and that was good to see.  There is still some big players with buying interest.  This is options expiration week so expect a volatile end of the trading week.</p>
<p><span id="more-7336"></span> Hold the line on current trades.</p>
<p>It&#8217;s as simple as that.  The RSI is bouncing off the 50 level after retreating to it.  It&#8217;s not like the RSI has to push through the 50, but it must stay above it.</p>
<p>I absolutely love the way the trades are acting.  Let&#8217;s play it smart and stick with these winners while waiting to carefully pick our next entries.</p>
