      <description><![CDATA[That&#8217;s the word for this market.  The sell-off lasted only a day.  I&#8217;d expect a bit more fireworks later this week &#8212; could provide a better entry point if you missed the move last week. The impulsive move from the &#8230; <a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/trading-the-market/resilient/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>That&#8217;s the word for this market.  The sell-off lasted only a day.  I&#8217;d expect a bit more fireworks later this week &#8212; could provide a better entry point if you missed the move last week.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/SP1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-7287" title="S&amp;P" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/SP1-300x176.png" alt="" width="300" height="176" /></a><span id="more-7286"></span>The impulsive move from the bottom (think straight up with no overlapping bars) tells me this market is not going to be giving easy entries.  I&#8217;ll try and be patient and pick my entry points with care.</p>
<p>This DJ Transportation chart shows the action that likely lies ahead for the major indexes.  The Transports have retraced the entire move since the April 29th high.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/Transports.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-7288" title="Transports" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/Transports-300x257.png" alt="" width="300" height="257" /></a></p>
<p>The NASDAQ brothers look especially frisky &#8211;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/NASDAQ.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-7289" title="NASDAQ" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/NASDAQ-300x254.png" alt="" width="300" height="254" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/NASDAQ-100.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-7290" title="NASDAQ 100" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/NASDAQ-100-300x252.png" alt="" width="300" height="252" /></a></p>
<p>Let&#8217;s continue to ride the ponies we have &#8212; they&#8217;re making money and only 3 have failed to hit their first profit target.  Continue to move the stops as I post them &#8212; when those stops are hit we&#8217;ll sell the remaining 1/2.  Hopefully we have some time to let these horses run!</p>
<p><a href="http://http://tiny.cc/z17je">Trade Sheet</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
