      <description><![CDATA[The big green candle was joined by higher volume on both the NASDAQ and NDX.  A good start toward a more constructive market and a higher low. The S&#38;P5oo seemed to take the move in stride and didn&#8217;t have the &#8230; <a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/uncategorized/todays-big-candle/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The big green candle was joined by higher volume on both the NASDAQ and NDX.  A good start toward a more constructive market and a higher low.</p>
<p>The S&amp;P5oo seemed to take the move in stride and didn&#8217;t have the strong volume push.  Nevertheless, all of the major averages are now trading above the 200d MA.</p>
<p>Let&#8217;s see if there is follow through to the upside or a pause in the next day or so.</p>
<p><span id="more-7194"></span>The RSI is crowding the 50 line.  Price may be about ready for a breather after two strong days for the junior averages and four in a row for the seniors.</p>
<p>A pullback or pause will provide the clue to get long.</p>
