    <item>
      <title>Wednesday Whipping</title>
      <link>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/uncategorized/wednesday-whipping/</link>
      <comments>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/uncategorized/wednesday-whipping/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jun 2011 03:52:39 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Range Trader</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/?p=7133</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[No follow through today.  A new lower low was made as price finally touched the 200d MA. The widely watched March low is coming into view.  Don&#8217;t be surprised if price doesn&#8217;t stop there.  This is a very tricky area &#8230; <a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/uncategorized/wednesday-whipping/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>No follow through today.  A new lower low was made as price finally touched the 200d MA.</p>
<p>The widely watched March low is coming into view.  Don&#8217;t be surprised if price doesn&#8217;t stop there.  This is a very tricky area to trade and best for long traders to keep their toes out of the water.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/SP-5005.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-7134" title="S&amp;P 500" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/SP-5005-300x273.png" alt="" width="300" height="273" /></a></p>
<p><span id="more-7133"></span> The VIX did close above 20.  Volume was high on this downbeat Wednesday.  Volatility has been elevated the last few sessions.</p>
<p>Panic selling may be just around the corner.  Even then it will take a couple of days to settle nerves.  The first pullback from the break out will be the best opportunity to jump on the long side.</p>
<p>Before then a lot needs to happen.</p>
<p>The short trades are working nicely.  Updated stops are on tonight&#8217;s trade sheet.</p>
<p><a href="http://tinyurl.com/4d3tfoc">Trade Sheet.</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
