      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Don&#8217;t let a pretty face turn your head, this is an ugly market!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Lipstick-pig.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-7092" title="Lipstick pig" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Lipstick-pig-244x300.png" alt="" width="244" height="300" /></a></p>
<p>Here&#8217;s the 15 minute chart I showed yesterday.  Price sliced through the shorter term trend lines and has come to rest and bounce this morning at the longer trend line.  The blue line marking the last pivot high was never challenged.  The upswing volume was weak, too.</p>
