<h2>This is an almost impossible market to trade, here&#8217;s why &#8211;  Long trades are <em>veeerrry</em> premature.  Short trades in an oversold market are a big risk.</h2>
<p>The 200d MA is getting closer, but will it provide a floor or just another level to slice through like a knife in warm butter?</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/SP3.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-7093" title="S&amp;P" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/SP3-300x281.png" alt="" width="300" height="281" /></a></p>
