    <item>
      <title>Quality As Important As Quantity</title>
      <link>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/trading-the-market/quality-important-quantity/</link>
      <comments>http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/trading-the-market/quality-important-quantity/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jun 2011 15:27:54 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Range Trader</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Trading The Market]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[short term market analysis]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/?p=7072</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[The market is using a familiar playbook and starting the day in the green.  The problem is it doesn&#8217;t close in the green. A weak market by itself is no reason to go short.  It&#8217;s important to judge the &#8220;quality&#8221; &#8230; <a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/trading-the-market/quality-important-quantity/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The market is using a familiar playbook and starting the day in the green.  The problem is it doesn&#8217;t close in the green.</p>
<p>A weak market by itself is no reason to go short.  It&#8217;s important to judge the &#8220;quality&#8221; of the weakness and get the timing right.</p>
<p>A market that&#8217;s been consistently beaten (like this one) creates problems.  Play the short side too soon and it will bounce.  Go long prematurely and it drops.</p>
<p>These are the times that will define your mettle as a trader.  Can you tough it out and wait for set ups and signals?  Do you have predetermined set ups and signals?</p>
<p>This is a 15 minute S&amp;P chart.  Lots of overhead resistance for this market to digest.  The white trend lines show that price is barely living on the top side of the short lines.</p>
<p>All eyes will be on the close.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/15-min.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-7073" title="15 min" src="http://www.rangetraders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/15-min-300x248.png" alt="" width="300" height="248" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
]]></content:encoded>
